  "bodyHtml": "<head><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><div style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px;\">\n\t<div style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span dir=\"ltr\">Dear Gregor</span></div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><span dir=\"ltr\">This is Anastassia again, the Product Owner of eKool. Just wanted to follow up and say thank you once again for your thorough report and suggestions. We absolutely appreciate the time and effort you’ve put into this.&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Here are a few comments from our CTO and development team that I wanted to forward.</div>\n<br><ul>\n<li><div dir=\"ltr\">\n<strong>Turnstile CAPTCHA</strong> will be reintroduced to the Registration form in eKool - it was indeed missed during a recent migration, and we acknowledge this oversight. Our developer is already working on restoring it. Thank you for reporting that.</div></li>\n<li><div dir=\"ltr\">Regarding the <strong>error messages</strong>, we’ve actually had extensive internal discussions on balancing out security and good user experience (UX). For example, the message that we currently have in our registration form, “User email already exists,” helps prevent user frustration during registration, especially for those who may have forgotten they already have an account (eKool is over 20+ years old). Masking this message and making the user fill out three pages of a signup form for nothing would lead to poor UX, unnecessary support tickets, and all-around confusion.</div></li>\n<li><div dir=\"ltr\">The same rationale applies to showing an alert if a <strong>personal ID code</strong> already exists. Many users no longer have access to their email, and this mechanism helps them identify if they’ve previously registered. We currently see no significant security risk from these single data points.</div></li>\n<li><div dir=\"ltr\">For the <strong>password reset form</strong>, we agree with your suggestion and will implement a more secure, non-revealing message.</div></li>\n<li><div>As for the <strong>email change form</strong>, this action occurs inside the user profile while the user is already authenticated. Since Turnstile is enforced at login, we believe additional CAPTCHA here is unnecessary.</div></li>\n<li><div dir=\"ltr\">Lastly, since March 2025, 2FA has been mandatory for all users upon login, and email confirmation has always been required upon registration - we believe these measures offer strong protection against fraudulent actors overall.</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Thank you again for your contribution to improving our platform’s security. Please don’t hesitate to reach out if you have any follow-up questions.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial\">With kindest regards,</div>\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"></div>\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">Anastassia Steffen</b></div>\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial\"><b dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">Product Owner of eKool</b></div>\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial\"><a href=\"https://contact.ekool.eu/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(44, 92, 197); text-decoration: none; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word\" target=\"_blank\">contact.ekool.eu</a></div>\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box\"></div>\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal;  text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 1.2\"><img src=\"https://eucattachment.freshdesk.com/inline/attachment?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpZCI6MTAxMjQyOTk5NjE2LCJkb21haW4iOiJla29vbC5mcmVzaGRlc2suY29tIiwiYWNjb3VudF9pZCI6MjQxNjU4M30.ZVvph8mlpe0wC91i96yn-hBYlKUpL2zOTscKzrY11AQ\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" height=\"38px\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; width: 111.946px\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\" data-id=\"101242999616\"></div>\n<br>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<span title=\"fd_tkt_identifier\" style=\"font-size:0px; font-family:&quot;fdtktid&quot;; min-height:0px; height:0px; opacity:0; max-height:0px; line-height:0px; colo